headline: Q4 Earnings Roundup: Bowlero (NYSE:BOWL) And The Rest Of The Consumer Discretionary Segment
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how consumer discretionary stocks fared in Q4, starting with Bowlero (NYSE:BOWL).
